{
  "stem": "1216.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I suppose so that the guards could see whether anybody was trying to escape or to count us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were forever counting us in Theresienstadt-- in Westerbork, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no selection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all herded directly into the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The gate consisted essentially of just wood  and barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were all herded through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we stood in line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Westerbork, we always stood in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing you could do where you didn't stand in line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this case, it was for the registration, so-called, and the medical examination, so-called.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the registration was simply looking at your papers and whether you had an S on your papers, which stood for the German word Strafe, punishment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you went into a different barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or to see whether the family was really all together [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] more than really anything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to make a note of your transport number, which became an ID number.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I supposed to keep, as Germans were want to do in those days, a card catalog of whoever was there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The medical examination, all I remember of it is we had to strip naked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, whether that was because they wanted to see that we were-- whether we were hiding something, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't offhand remember actually being examined, but we might have been.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
